text.tspan: New Staff may be employed if:· At any particular time the requirement exceeds the availability figure e.g. in case of induction of new vessels into the management.· The requirement necessitates staff with more experience and qualification than those available as per the availability list.· The staff as per the availability list is unable to join due to some reason.In such cases the database of new applicants in Phoenix shall be first verified for availability and suitability. If suitable candidates are not available, the following measures shall be taken as appropriate:1) Advertisements in Seaman’s club for officers and Seamen’s boarding house for ratings2) Visits by superintendents to reputed organizations/ colleges and interview the prospective candidates attending college/ courses asand when required.3) Advertisements in Newspapers and/or other publications in case of large and urgent requirement4) Company’s Website/ Recruitment Websites5) Any other locationThe selection process shall commence by making the applicant fill in the stipulated application form OC 9. The accuracy of the datafilled in shall be verified against the applicant’s original documents such as the seaman’s book, passport, licenses, STCWendorsements and Training Certificates.The recruitment process is outlined in the flow chart below:During the recruitment process besides giving consideration to the past experience a reference check shall also be carried out fromhis previous employers where possible.Competency Assessment of Officers and Ratings is carried out at the Training Institute / Manning office as part of the Pre-joiningprocess.Proficiency in English shall be determined by the Assessing officer during the interview process and documented in the EvaluationQuestionnaire in Phoenix.4.15.3APPROVAL OF STAFFMinimum Approval Levels are as follows:RankExisting staffNew Recruits and on PromotionMaster and Chief EngineerGeneral ManagerGeneral Manager Chief Officer and Second Engineer Technical/ Marine Superintendent General ManagerJunior Officers Technical/ Marine Superintendent Technical/ Marine Superintendent BosunMarine / Technical Superintendent Marine / Technical Superintendent RatingsFleet Personnel Superintendent/ Assistant Crewing Manager Fleet Personnel Superintendent/ Assistant Crewing Manager
